{
  "stem": "20745.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we still didn't believe-- we didn't know where are we going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told us where-- that we going to the ammunition factory, but we-- we didn't know anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- I didn't want to jump.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the doors opened up, there were police, their police, Germans, and-- and they took us to this camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were three camps, barrack A, barrack B, and barrack C.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A was the best one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The B was-- I don't know, but-- but the C, they put in the-- the-- in the-- in the-- we made a shelf.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the guns, they put in the powder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, but they-- and the people got so yellow, they didn't have a bed-- a shower [? thing. ?] They used to take us to our camp to get showers, take showers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were so yellow, like an egg yolk, from the powder, from the gun powder.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in camp A.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, was a big, big place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us with the-- with guards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us in the morning, and they brought-- and we came back at night, also with guards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But one week, I-- I worked nights-- they worked 24 hours a day-- and one week, days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was different, with smaller barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were smaller barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we could go outside and-- outside and talk to friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're talking about what we talk about what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's nothing else to talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had nobody, no-- they gave us food, a little better than Majdanek, a sweet soup every day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the coffee in the morning, the same thing, a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About the same.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they made selections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told us to-- I-- to go outside and to line up.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
